@NiceLittleRabbit
Since the data are demo, Jepp will not provide for old and new cycle i.e. it will not automatically cut over on effective date to the new data so only one db is catered. So you will load new data only on or after effective date. You can load from db_a or db_b on effective date and check which one is the newer one. That is my guess.
